data.description: Bright and airy split-level offers 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths along with an updated kitchen and all appliances! Decent living room and dining room!    One year old New Roof.  16 x 14 primary bedroom has wall-length closet and a beautifully updated bath with raised vanity and walk in shower! Lower level family room offers loads of space and sliding glass doors that lead to the patio! Third full bath on lower level!  Across the yard you'll find a neighborhood park and you don't have to cross a  single street to get there!  Two car attached garage!  Concrete front steps, sidewalk and garage floor. Microwave (2016)! Furnace Home being sold "as is".
